  gem.meaning_content = "Angel Aura Quartz is a super precious stone with high vibrational energy. It is said to connect us with higher realms and angelic energies. It has a gentle yet powerful energy that can bring a sense of peace and calm.\n\nThe light reflections on its surface give it an angelic appearance, which is how it got its name. In this guide we learn everything about Angel Aura Quartz, right from its meaning, healing benefits, uses and cleansing ways.\nLet’s get started!\n\nTable of Contents\n\nToggle\n\n• What is the meaning of Angel Aura Quartz\n• What is Angel Aura Quartz?\n• Science and origin of Angel Aura Quartz\n• Healing properties of Angel Aura Quartz\n• Emotional healing properties of Angel Aura Quartz\n• Physical healing properties of Angel Aura Quartz\n• Mental healing properties of Angel Aura Quartz\n• Spiritual healing properties of Angel Aura Quartz\n\n• Angel Aura Quartz meaning and chakra connection\n• Best crystals to pair with Angel Aura Quartz\n• How to identify a real Angel Aura Quartz\n• How to use Angel Aura Quartz?\n• How to cleanse and recharge Angel Aura Quartz?\n\n## What is the meaning of Angel Aura Quartz\n\nThe meaning of Angel Aura Quartz is “stone of the angels”. It is said to be a powerful stone for connecting with angels and other higher beings. This crystal has a very high vibration and is believed to be helpful in opening the third eye and crown chakras.\n\nAngel Aura Quartz is known to be helpful in accessing past lives and in understanding the karmic lessons from those lives.\n\nThis crystal attracts and maintains love relationships. It is one of those crystals that are helpful in releasing anger and resentment.\n\nIn brief the meaning of Angel Aura Quartz can be defined as below:\n\n– Stone of the angels\n\n– Powerful stone for connecting with angels and other higher beings\n\n– Helps in accessing past lives\n\n– Helps in understanding the karmic lessons\n\n– Attracts and maintains love relationships\n\n– Releases anger and resentment\n\n## What is Angel Aura Quartz?\n\nAngel Aura Quartz is a type of quartz that has been artificially enhanced with metals. The most common metals used are platinum and silver, but other metals may be used as well. This creates a beautiful iridescent sheen on the surface of the quartz.\n\nAngel Aura Quartz is said to have sweet and gentle energy that can bring a sense of peace and calm. It is also said to be a powerful stone for connecting with angels and other higher beings.\n\nAngel Aura Quartz meaning is derived from its beautiful appearance. The word “aura” refers to the energy field that surrounds us. This energy field can be seen as a light around the body. “Angel” refers to the higher beings that are said to surround us and guide us. Therefore, Angel Aura Quartz is said to be a stone that can help us connect with our angels and other higher beings.\n\nThe Angel Aura Quartz properties are said to be similar to those of Clear Quartz. Clear Quartz is known as the “master healer” and is said to be a powerful stone for amplifying energy and intention. This is why Angel Aura Quartz is also said to be a powerful stone for amplifying energy and intention. It is also said to be a stone of peace and calm.\n\nImage by Etsy.com\n\n## Science and origin of Angel Aura Quartz\n\nAngel Aura Quartz is a type of quartz that has been artificially enhanced with metals. The most common metals used are platinum and silver, but other metals may be used as well. This creates a beautiful iridescent sheen on the surface of the quartz.\n\nAngel Aura Quartz is found in a number of locations around the world, including Brazil, Madagascar, and the United States.\n\nThe first recorded use of Angel Aura Quartz dates back to the early 1900s.\n\n## Healing properties of Angel Aura Quartz\n\nThis crystal is capable of many healing benefits. It radiates a very high level of positivity and can help to raise your mood and energy levels. It is also said to be helpful in reducing stress and anxiety.\n\nAngel Aura Quartz has emotional healing benefits along with physical, mental and spiritual benefits. Let us get into more details about Angel Aura Quartz healing benefits.\n\n## Emotional healing properties of Angel Aura Quartz\n\nWhen one feels overwhelmed with negative emotions, this crystal can help to soothe and calm the emotions. It can also help to release repressed emotions. Angel Aura Quartz can be used by those who have difficulty expressing their emotions. It can help to open up the heart chakra and allow emotions to flow freely.\n\n1. Aids in getting a deeper understanding of yourself\n\n2. Release of stress and anxiety\n\n3. Soothing of negative emotions\n\n4. Opening of the heart chakra\n\n5. Amplification of energy and intention\n\n6. Connecting with angels and higher beings\n\n7. Bringing a sense of peace and calm\n\n## Physical healing properties of Angel Aura Quartz\n\nMany of the physical health problems arise from stress and worries. Stress is one of those dangerous ailments that can lead to various other health problems if not dealt with in time. Angel Aura Quartz can help to reduce stress and tension in the body. It can also help to improve circulation and digestion.\n\n1. Reducing stress and tension\n\n2. Improving circulation\n\n3. Improving digestion\n\n4. Aiding in detoxification\n\n5. Boosting the immune system\n\n6. Reducing inflammation\n\n7. Reducing pain\n\n8. Supporting the respiratory system\n\n## Mental healing properties of Angel Aura Quartz\n\nAngel Aura Quartz can help to clear the mind and allow for better focus and concentration. It can also help to reduce mental chatter and worry. This crystal can also be helpful for those who suffer from mental disorders such as anxiety and depression.\n\n1. Clearing the mind\n\n2. Improving focus and concentration\n\n3. Reducing mental chatter\n\n4. Reducing worry and anxiety\n\n5. Helping with mental disorders\n\n## Spiritual healing properties of Angel Aura Quartz\n\nAngel Aura Quartz is a crystal that can help with spiritual transformation. Using its pure and positive vibrations, it can help to open up the chakras and cleanse the auric field. It can also help to raise your vibration and connect you with your higher self.\n\n1. Spiritual transformation\n\n2. Opening of the chakras\n\n3. Cleaning of the auric field\n\n4. Raising of vibration\n\n5. Connection with the higher self\n\n6. Protection from negative energy\n\n## Angel Aura Quartz meaning and chakra connection\n\nAngel Aura Quartz is a stone that is said to be helpful for all chakras. However, it is especially connected to the crown chakra. The crown chakra is the chakra that is responsible for our connection with the divine. It is also the chakra of our highest truth and purpose.\n\nAngel Aura Quartz can help to open and balance the crown chakra. It can also help to cleanse and purify the chakras. By doing this, it can help to bring us into alignment with our highest truth and purpose.\n\nThe Angel Aura Quartz properties are also said to be helpful for the heart chakra. The heart chakra is the chakra of love, compassion and forgiveness. Angel Aura Quartz on the other hand is known as the stone of peace and calm. It can help to open up the heart chakra and allow us to give and receive love more easily.\n\nAngel Aura Quartz also connects with the throat chakra. The throat chakra is the chakra of communication and self-expression. Angel Aura Quartz can help to open up the throat chakra and allow us to express ourselves more easily.\n\n## Best crystals to pair with Angel Aura Quartz\n\nAngel Aura Quartz pairs well with many other crystals. Some of the best crystals to pair with Angel Aura Quartz are:\n\n1. Clear Quartz\n\n2. Rose Quartz\n\n3. Celestite\n\n4. Lithium Quartz\n\n5. Morganite\n\nEach of these crystals has its own unique properties and energies. Clear Quartz is known as the master healer and is said to be a powerful stone for amplifying energy and intention. \n\nRose Quartz is the stone of love and is helpful for opening up the heart chakra. Celestite is a stone of peace and calm and works on reducing stress and anxiety. Lithium Quartz provides balance and is believed to be helpful for bringing the chakras into alignment. Morganite is a stone of compassion and is said to be helpful for opening up the heart chakra.\n\nPairing Angel Aura Quartz with these crystals can amplify Angel Aura Quartz meaning and the energies of both stones. It can also help to create more balanced and harmonious energy.\n\n## How to identify a real Angel Aura Quartz\n\nThere are many imitations and fake stones on the market. It is important to be able to identify a real Angel Aura Quartz so that you don’t end up with a fake stone.\n\n• One way to tell if a stone is a real Angel Aura Quartz is to look at the surface. A real Angel Aura Quartz will have a beautiful iridescent sheen on the surface. This sheen is created by the metals that are used to enhance the quartz. If the stone you are looking at does not have this sheen, then it is most likely not a real Angel Aura Quartz.\n\n• Another way to tell if a stone is real Angel Aura Quartz is to look at the colour. A real Angel Aura Quartz has a beautiful rainbow of colours. The colours will be very vibrant and shimmering. If the stone you are looking at does not have these colours, then it is most likely not a real Angel Aura Quartz.\n\n• A real Angel Aura Quartz will also be very clear. If the stone you are looking at is not clear, then it may not be a real Angel Aura Quartz.\n\n• If you are unsure if the stone you are looking at is a real Angel Aura Quartz, then you can always consult with a certified crystal\n\n## How to use Angel Aura Quartz?\n\nAngel Aura Quartz meaning is defined from its ability to act as an aura cleanser. It helps in getting rid of the negative emotions and clearing your surroundings for positive vibes to flow in. Having this crystal around you will provide a peaceful and calming vibration. \n\nThere are many ways to use Angel Aura Quartz. Some of the most popular ways are:\n\n• Carry it with you: You can carry Angel Aura Quartz with you in your pocket or in a small pouch. This will allow you to benefit from its energies throughout the day.\n\n• Place it in your home: You can place Angel Aura Quartz in different areas of your home. Corners at home where you might need positive energy or a place where you are more often seated are the best places to keep this crystal.\n\n• Make it into jewellery: You can make Angel Aura Quartz into jewellery such as a necklace, bracelet or ring. This will ensure you benefit from its energies while also having a beautiful piece of jewellery. This is one of the most common ways of using it.\n\n• Meditate with it: You can meditate with Angel Aura Quartz by holding it in your hand or placing it on your forehead. Meditating with Angel Aura Quartz helps with the overall spiritual journey and your focus and concentration become sharper.\n\n• Use it in crystal healing: You can use Angel Aura Quartz in crystal healing. This can be done by placing it on the chakras or by using it in grid work. Many practitioners are believed to be using it for healing purposes.\n\n## How to cleanse and recharge Angel Aura Quartz?\n\nAngel Aura Quartz can be cleansed using many different methods. Some of the most popular methods are:\n\n1. Sunlight: You can cleanse Angel Aura Quartz by placing it in direct sunlight for a few hours. Remove the crystal after a few hours and wipe it with a soft, dry cotton cloth. You may also use affirmations during this process.\n\n2. Moonlight: Moonlight is one of the most gentle and harmless ways of cleansing and recharging your crystal. All you have to do is place your crystal outside during a full moon night. Remove it in the morning and it is ready to be used. You can also place it in the moonlight overnight on a full moon day.\n\n3. Running water: You can also cleanse Angel Aura Quartz by running it under lukewarm water for a few minutes. Pat the crystal dry and it is ready to be used again. \n\n4. Salt water: Using salt water is another way of cleansing Angel Aura Quartz. You can either add the crystal to a bowl of salt water or make a salt water solution and add the crystal to it. Leave the crystal in the salt water for a few minutes before removing it. Rinse the crystal under lukewarm water and pat it dry.\n\n5. Smudging: Smudging is a popular method of cleansing. You can use any herb or plant that you like for this purpose. Some of the most popular herbs used for smudging are sage, sweetgrass and cedar. To smudge Angel Aura Quartz, hold the crystal in your hand and pass it through the smoke of the smudging herb. \n\n6. Burying: Burying is another popular method of cleansing. You can bury the crystal in the ground for a few days. Remove it after a few days and wipe it with a cotton cloth. \n\n7. Sound: A Sound is a powerful tool that can be used for cleansing. You can use a singing bowl, gong or any other instrument that you like. Hold the crystal in your hand and pass it through the sound waves.\n\n8. Affirmations: Affirmations are positive statements that can be used to cleanse and charge your crystal. Some of the affirmations that you can use for Angel Aura Quartz are:\n\n• I release all negativity from my Angel Aura Quartz\n\n• My Angel Aura Quartz is cleansed and charged\n\n• My Angel Aura Quartz is filled with positive energy\n\n• I am surrounded by the love and light of my angels\n\n• My Angel Aura Quartz is a powerful tool for amplifying my energy and intention\n\n• My Angel Aura Quartz is a powerful tool for connecting with my angels\n\nBest method is to use affirmations with one of the above cleansing ways. This amplifies the overall cleansing and recharging of the crystal.\n\nYou may also want to learn about other Quartz like the Garden Quartz and its healing benefits. Read on and give us your comments."
