if gem = Gemstone.find_by(slug: "black-obsidian")
  gem.meaning_content = "Black obsidian is a wonderful crystal that can be used in many different ways. Its dark and mysterious appearance is often associated with the underworld, and it is said to be a powerful stone that can help one to connect with the energy of the Earth.\n\nFor ages, black obsidian has been used for scrying or predicting the future. When it comes to Feng Shui, black obsidian is often used to create a protective barrier around the home.\n\nLearn all about black obsidian meaning, healing properties, benefits and uses, and how this amazing crystal can help you to achieve your goals.\n\nTable of Contents\n\nToggle\n\n• What is Obsidian?\n• What is Black Obsidian?\n• Black Obsidian Meaning\n• Origin and History of Black Obsidian stones\n• Black Obsidian Properties – Physical\n• Black Obsidian crystal Healing Properties\n• Emotional healing properties of Black obsidian stone\n• Physical healing properties of Black obsidian stone\n• Spiritual healing properties of Black Obsidian stone\n• Metaphysical properties of Black obsidian stone\n\n• Black Obsidian Chakra Connections\n• What is black obsidian good for?\n• Black Obsidian Crystal Combinations\n• How To Cleanse Black Obsidian?\n• Recharging Black Obsidian using affirmations:\n• How to use Black Obsidian?\n• Obsidian at work\n• Black Obsidian at home\n• Obsidian as jewellery\n• Carry Black Obsidian in your pocket\n• Black Obsidian as a worry stone\n• Meditation with Black Obsidian\n• Black Obsidian as Crystal grids\n\n• Black Obsidian Zodiac sign\n• Is Obsidian a lucky stone?\n• What is the difference between Snowflake Obsidian and Black Obsidian stones\n• Black Tourmaline vs Black Obsidian What is the difference?\n\n## What is Obsidian?\n\nObsidian is a natural glass formed as an extrusive igneous rock. It is produced when felsic lava extruded from a volcano cools rapidly with minimal crystal growth. Obsidian is commonly found within the margins of rhyolitic lava flows known as obsidian flows, where the chemical composition (high silica content) causes a high viscosity, which, upon rapid cooling, forms a natural glass from the lava.\n\nObsidian comes in many colors. The most common colors are black, dark brown, dark green, and grey. The colors are caused by the presence of different elements in the lava. For example, iron and magnesium give the obsidian a dark green color, while sodium gives obsidian a dark brown or black color.\n\n## What is Black Obsidian?\n\nBlack Obsidian is a form of Obsidian and is a natural glass that is formed from the molten lava of volcanoes, hence also known as volcanic glass. It is an extremely powerful and intense stone. It can be used for protection, as it is known to block negative energies. It is also known to cleanse the aura and to help release negative patterns and behaviours.\n\nThe name “obsidian” comes from the Latin word “obsidianus”, which means “dark stone”. Black obsidian is also sometimes called “dragon’s glass”.\n\nBlack obsidian is found in many different parts of the world, including the United States, Mexico, and Iceland.\n\n## Black Obsidian Meaning\n\nThe name ‘Black Obsidian’ refers to a dark-colored natural glass that acts as an absorber. Black Obsidian meaning stands for\n\n* Protection\n\n* Transformation\n\n* Manifestation\n\nThis gemstone is often used for scrying, which is a type of divination. Scrying is done by gazing into the stone in order to see visions of the past, present, or future.\n\nBlack Obsidian is also the stone of protection. It is thought to absorb negative energy and help shield the wearer from emotional and physical harm.\n\n## Origin and History of Black Obsidian stones\n\nBlack Obsidian is a natural volcanic glass that was first discovered in Ethiopia. This crystal has been in use since ancient times, and it is one of the most popular crystals in the world. It has been used in jewelry, sculptures, and other art forms.\n\nThis crystal is also known as the “Wizard’s Stone”, “Obsidian Stone”, or “Black Stone”. It is said to be a very powerful crystal that can help one in their spiritual journey.\n\nIt has a historic significance because it has been used in many different cultures for its healing properties.\n\nSome of the most notable cultures that have used Black Obsidian are the Egyptians, the Mayans, and the Aztecs.\n\nThe Egyptians used it in their jewelry and amulets. They believed that this crystal had the power to protect them from evil spirits. The Egyptians used it as a protective stone from negative energy.\n\nThe Mayans used Black Obsidian in their ceremonies and rituals. They believed that it had the power to connect them with the spirit world.\n\nThe Aztecs used Black Obsidian for scrying. They would use it to look into the future and to make predictions.\n\nThe ancient peoples created arrowheads from Black Obsidian. They believed that it had the power to kill the enemy.\n\n## Black Obsidian Properties – Physical\n\n-Black Obsidian is a type of natural glass formed from volcanic lava, hence known as volcanic glass stone.\n\n-It is usually found in the form of small, rounded pebbles or large nodules.\n\n-It has a smooth, glossy surface yet sharp edges with a vitreous or glassy luster.\n\n-The color of Black Obsidian can range from deep black to dark brown.\n\n-It is a relatively soft stone with a Mohs hardness of 5 to 5.5.\n\n## Black Obsidian crystal Healing Properties\n\nBlack Obsidian is a powerful protection stone that can be used for healing, protection, and self-reflection. It is a powerful stone that helps to cleanse the aura and protect against negative energy. Black Obsidian healing properties are widely known for their grounding and centring effect. It promotes calmness and serenity.\n\nThis black stone being born from volcanos has very strong energy. It has the energy of the earth and is very grounding. It is also a stone of protection, helping to guard against negative energy and psychic attack. Black Obsidian is known for its emotional, physical and spiritual healing benefits.\n\n## Emotional healing properties of Black obsidian stone\n\n– Absorbs negative energy\n\n– Acts as a shield to keep the aura positive\n\n– Aids in letting go of unwanted energy\n\n– Releases fear and self-doubts\n\n– Promotes strength, courage, and determination\n\nBlack Obsidian stone is the protector of emotions. Our emotions play a very important role in our lives, and they can be very powerful. They can be the source of our strength and our courage, or they can be the source of our fears and doubts. When we are faced with challenges in our lives, it is our emotions that will often dictate how we react.\n\nIf we allow our emotions to get the best of us, we can often find ourselves feeling overwhelmed and defeated. However, if we can learn to control our emotions and use them to our advantage, we can often find the strength and courage to overcome any obstacle. A Black obsidian stone is one such magical crystal that helps in bringing balance to the emotion\n\nBlack Obsidian is a strong stone that can help us to release any negative emotions that are holding us back. It can also help to protect us from negative energy and shows inner reflection. This stone can also help to keep our aura positive. When we are surrounded by positive energy, we are more likely to feel positive ourselves. This strongly protective stone ensures that negative energies stay away from your mind and emotions.\n\nBlack Obsidian can also be used to help us let go of any unwanted emotions. Often, we hold onto emotions that no longer serve us. These emotions can be toxic and can weigh us down. By letting go of these emotions, we can free ourselves from their negative effects.\n\n## Physical healing properties of Black obsidian stone\n\nBlack Obsidian is known to be helpful in treating the following physical ailments:\n\n-Aching muscles\n\n-Arthritis\n\n-Digestive disorders\n\n-High blood pressure\n\n-Insect bites\n\n-Skin problems\n\nApart from its emotional healing benefits, Black Obsidian is widely known for its physical healing properties. This stone acts as a detoxifier for the body and helps get rid of the toxins within it. It is great for the immune system as well and helps to keep it functioning properly. Those who feel low on energy can also benefit from this stone as it helps to increase one’s vitality. Black obsidian stone is a wonderful crystal for those on their healing journey. It helps in expediting the healing process.\n\n## Spiritual healing properties of Black Obsidian stone\n\n-Aids in past life recall\n\n-Helps with psychic development\n\n-Aids in astral travel\n\n-Facilitates shamanic journeying\n\n-Helps one to connect with their higher self\n\n-Access hidden knowledge\n\n-Stimulates the root chakra\n\n-Grounds and protects one during spiritual work\n\nBlack Obsidian is a very powerful and protective stone and is excellent for use in meditation or shamanic journeying. It helps one to connect with their higher self and to access hidden knowledge. It can be used to stimulate the root chakra and to ground and protect one during spiritual work which provides deep soul healing.\n\nIts spiritual properties blocks psychic attacks and help to cleanse and purify one’s aura.\n\nBlack Obsidian is also said to assist one in releasing attachments, addictions, compulsions and negative patterns. It can also be used for protection from negative energy and for cleansing and purifying one’s auric field.\n\nThe physical and spiritual body are linked and when the spiritual energy is strong, it can have a positive effect on the physical body. The reverse is also true, when the physical body is unwell, it can have a negative effect on the spiritual body.\n\nIf you are looking for a stone to help you with your spiritual quest, Black Obsidian would be an excellent choice.\n\n## Metaphysical properties of Black obsidian stone\n\n-Aids in grounding and protection\n\n-Brings courage during difficult times\n\n-Helps one to let go of the past\n\n-Fosters a deep connection with the Earth\n\n-Encourages self-control\n\n-Promotes spiritual growth\n\nThe metaphysical properties of this stone are quite strong. Black Obsidian is a powerful stone that helps to cleanse and purify the aura. It can also aid in protection from negative energies. Black Obsidian can help to ground and bring the wearer closer to earth’s energy. It is also a stone of courage, helping one to face difficult times in life. Black Obsidian can also help to foster a deep connection with the Earth.\n\nBlack Obsidian is an excellent stone for those who are seeking spiritual growth. It can help to promote self-control and to let go of the past. Black Obsidian is also a stone of protection, helping to keep one safe from harm.\n\n## Black Obsidian Chakra Connections\n\nBlack Obsidian crystal is connected to the Root Chakra. The root chakra is located at the base of the spine and is responsible for our feeling of safety and security. It is also connected to our survival instincts and our fight-or-flight response. When the root chakra is aligned it gives us a sense of calm and grounding. We feel safe and secure in our environment and are able to face challenging situations with ease.\n\nBlack Obsidian helps in aligning the root chakra and ensuring it is never out of balance. It is also a very protective stone, making it a great choice for anyone who feels they are being attacked energetically.\n\n## What is black obsidian good for?\n\n1. Black obsidian is excellent for clearing the aura and for grounding. It is also a very powerful stone for protection.\n\n2. This crystal can help one to release fears and negativity. It is also helpful in providing strength during times of change.\n\n3. Black obsidian can also assist in balancing the yin and yang energies.\n\n4. This stone can also help to promote self-control, willpower and discipline.\n\n5. Black obsidian can also be used to cleanse and purify the auric field.\n\n6. This crystal can also be used to promote psychic abilities and visions.\n\n7. Black obsidian is also excellent for scrying.\n\n8. This stone can also be used to relieve pain.\n\n9. Black obsidian can also help to reduce stress and tension.\n\n10. This crystal can also be used to promote fertility.\n\n## Black Obsidian Crystal Combinations\n\nBlack obsidian can be combined with other stones for a variety of purposes.\n\nWith Carnelian:\n\nCarnelian is a great stone to use with black obsidian when you are working on manifesting your goals. The combination of these two stones will help you to take action towards your goals and make them a reality.\n\nWith Citrine:\n\nCitrine is a stone of abundance and black obsidian can help you to release any negativity or blockages that are preventing you from achieving your goals. This combination is known for attracting wealth and abundance into your life.\n\nWith Clear Quartz:\n\nClear quartz is a stone of clarity and black obsidian can help to remove any negativity or blockages that are clouding your judgement. This combination helps in making decisions and gaining clarity on your path.\n\nWith Tigers Eye:\n\nTigers eye is a stone of courage and black obsidian can help to release any fears or doubts that are holding you back. This combination is great for boosting your confidence and taking action towards your goals.\n\n## How To Cleanse Black Obsidian?\n\nIt is important to cleanse Obsidian frequently. Our crystals absorb the toxic energy and release protective energy. In this process, the crystals can become overloaded and will need to be cleansed. There are a few different ways that you can cleanse your Black Obsidian gemstone.\n\n1. Using water: You can cleanse your Black Obsidian by running it under cool water for a few minutes. Water is one of the most effective ways to cleanse gemstones as it\n\ncan remove negative energy and restore the stone’s natural vibration.\n\n2. Using salt: Another way to cleanse your Black Obsidian is by using salt. Simply place your stone in a bowl of salt for 24 hours. The salt will absorb any negative energy\n\nfrom the stone and leave it feeling refreshed and rejuvenated.\n\n3. Using sage: Sage is a powerful cleansing herb that is often used to cleanse gemstones. Simply hold your Black Obsidian in the smoke of a burning sage stick for a few minutes.\n\nThe sage will remove any negative energy from the stone and leave it feeling refreshed and cleansed.\n\n4. Using Sunlight: You can also cleanse your Black Obsidian by placing it in direct sunlight for a few hours. The sun’s rays will purify the stone and remove any negative energy it has been holding. While using sunlight to cleanse the crystal is an effective way, it is important to note that some stones can fade in color when exposed to direct sunlight for extended periods of time.\n\nMake sure you do not leave your Black Obsidian in the sun for too long as it could cause the stone to fade.\n\n5. Using moonlight: You can also cleanse your Black Obsidian by placing it in the moonlight overnight. The moon’s energy is very cleansing and will purify the stone of any negative energy it has been holding.\n\nOnce you have cleansed your Black Obsidian, it is important to charge it with positive energy. This can be done by placing it in a sunny window or by holding it in your hands and visualizing white light charging the stone.\n\n## Recharging Black Obsidian using affirmations:\n\nUsing affirmations is another great way to charge your Black Obsidian with positive energy. Simply hold the stone in your hands and repeat a positive affirmation such as “I am\n\nhealthy and happy” or “I am surrounded by love and light”. Repeating these affirmations will infuse the stone with positive energy and help to manifest your desires.\n\n## How to use Black Obsidian?\n\nThere are many ways to use Black Obsidian stone. Using this crystal in the right manner can help to achieve desired goals\n\n## Obsidian at work\n\nBlack Obsidian can be used at work to help with focus and concentration. Many believe keeping Black Obsidian at work helps in achieving goals. It provides the wearer with the strength to face challenges head-on and the courage to take risks. All the stress and tension at work can be dealt with by meditating with Black Obsidian.\n\n## Black Obsidian at home\n\nPlace one in the North East corner of your home to create a strong foundation and ward off any negativity that might enter your home. It is also placed at the front door to protect your home from negative energy. Keeping Black Obsidian at home helps to cleanse the space and keep the energy positive.\n\n## Obsidian as jewellery\n\nBlack Obsidian makes a beautiful jewellery piece. It can be used as a ring, pendant, bracelet or earring. When wearing Obsidian crystal, it stays close to the body and therefore, its energies are constantly at work.\n\nGiven the color of this stone is black, it goes with any other metal combination. however, it is often seen with silver as the metal. Gold is also used as it gives a regal look to the stone.\n\nMy personal favourite is the Black Obsidian bracelet. It looks stunning and also has a very powerful energy. Wear black obsidian for keeping yourself away from unwanted energy.\n\n## Carry Black Obsidian in your pocket\n\nAnother way to use Black Obsidian is to carry it in your pocket. This is a great way to have the crystal close to your body at all times. It is believed that when carrying Black Obsidian, one can benefit from its protective energies and it works well for finances.\n\n## Black Obsidian as a worry stone\n\nA worry stone is a smooth stone that is usually oval or teardrop-shaped. It is meant to be held in the hand and rubbed when feeling anxious or stressed.\n\nBlack Obsidian can be made into a worry stone. It is a great way to use the crystal when feeling overwhelmed. The act of rubbing the stone can help to ease the mind and body.\n\n## Meditation with Black Obsidian\n\nBlack Obsidian can be used during meditation to help one connect with the subconscious mind. While meditating, hold the crystal in your palm and visualize all the negativity, fears, and doubts disappearing into the stone. Feel Obsidian’s vibrations flowing through the body.\n\nAs you meditate, imagine a bright light emanating from the stone and filling your entire body with positivity.\n\n## Black Obsidian as Crystal grids\n\nBlack Obsidian can be used in crystal grids for protection or for banishing negative energy from a space.\n\nTo make a grid for protection, start by placing a Black Obsidian in the center of the grid. Then, surround it with other protective stones like Tourmaline, Amber, or Jet.\n\nTo make a grid for banishing negative energy, start by placing a Black Obsidian in the center of the grid. Then, surround it with other stones that have similar properties like Smokey Quartz or Hematite.\n\n## Black Obsidian Zodiac sign\n\nWhile anybody can use Black Obsidian, this stone is said to be particularly helpful for those who are working on their shadow self. It is also said to be a powerful stone for those who are born under the Scorpio zodiac sign. Those born under the sign of Scorpio are known for their intense and passionate nature, and Black Obsidian is said to help them channel this energy in a positive way.\n\n## Is Obsidian a lucky stone?\n\nBlack Obsidian is not traditionally considered a lucky stone, but it is thought to be helpful in bringing good luck to those who are willing to work hard for it. It is also said to be helpful in keeping away bad luck and negative energy.\n\n## What is the difference between Snowflake Obsidian and Black Obsidian stones\n\nBlack obsidian is formed from volcanic lava. It is usually a dark black color with a glossy sheen, shiny surface and sharp edges. Snowflake obsidian is a type of obsidian that contains small white “snowflake” markings. The major difference between these two types of obsidian is their appearance.\n\nThe formation process of snowflake obsidian is a little different than black obsidian. Snowflake obsidian is created when tiny gas bubbles become trapped in the lava as it cools. The gas bubbles cause the formation of small white “snowflake” markings.\n\n## Black Tourmaline vs Black Obsidian What is the difference?\n\nBlack Tourmaline is a type of Tourmaline, which is a semi-precious stone. Black Obsidian is a type of Obsidian, is a type of volcanic glass.\n\nBoth stones are black, but Black Tourmaline is usually opaque, while Black Obsidian is often translucent with very sharp edges. Black Tourmaline is also often found in crystal form, while Black Obsidian is usually found in rock form.\n\nBlack Obsidian is a powerful stone that can help to cleanse and protect your aura. It can also help to ground you and provide you with a sense of stability. Black Tourmaline can also help to cleanse and protect your aura, but it is also known for its ability to promote healing and balance.\n\nWant to explore other protective stones? Learn all about Black Onyx"
