if gem = Gemstone.find_by(slug: "fancy-jasper")
  gem.meaning_content = "All Jasper crystals are excellent nurturing stones. Fancy Jasper is no different. It is a crystal filled with healing benefits. Fancy Jasper meaning stands for relaxation and contentment, providing comfort and security, strength and healing. \n\nIts steady frequency calms the mind and grounds the emotions. It is a wonderful support for those who are prone to anxiety or worry.\n\nFancy Jasper is part of the Jasper family, which is a large group of minerals that come in many different colors and patterns. This wonderful stone has many healing properties and is known for the benefits that it provides to the wearer. \n\nIn this guide, I have covered everything from Fancy Jasper meaning to uses and benefits to best crystal combinations. By the end of this guide, you will know everything there is to know about Fancy Jasper. \n\nTable of Contents\n\nToggle\n\n• What is Fancy Jasper?\n• What is the meaning of Fancy Jasper?\n• Benefits of Fancy Jasper\n• Fancy Jasper and the chakra connection\n• Healing benefits of Fancy Jasper\n• Emotional healing benefits of Fancy Jasper\n• Physical healing benefits of Fancy Jasper\n• Metaphysical properties of Fancy Jasper:\n\n• What are the different ways to use Fancy Jasper?\n• Ways to cleanse Fancy Jasper\n• Best stone combinations to use with Fancy Jasper\n\n## What is Fancy Jasper?\n\nFancy Jasper is a type of Jasper that is characterized by its colorful patterns. It is a type of chalcedony which is a microcrystalline quartz. Fancy Jasper can be found in a variety of colors including red, yellow, green, blue and purple. \n\nThe patterns on Fancy Jasper are created by the different colors of the stone. These patterns can be abstract or they can resemble landscapes or other scenes.\n\nJasper is an opaque, impure variety of silica, usually red, yellow, brown or green in color; and rarely blue. The common red color is due to iron inclusions. \n\nThe mineral breaks with a smooth surface and is used for ornamentation or as a gemstone. It can be highly polished and is used for vases, seals and snuff boxes. Small statues have been carved from jasper (sometimes referred to as “picture jasper”) and it has also been used for intaglio and hardstone cameo engravings.\n\nFancy Jasper is found in a number of locations around the world including Australia, Brazil, Canada, China, India, Russia and the United States.\n\n## What is the meaning of Fancy Jasper?\n\nFancy Jasper is known as the “supreme Nurturer”. It sustains and supports during times of stress, and brings tranquillity and wholeness. Jasper provides protection and balances yin and yang. It grounds energies and rectifies unjust situations.\n\nFancy Jasper meaning is derived from its ability to provide emotional strength and stability during difficult times. It is a stone of gentleness and relaxation, bringing peace and calm to those who wear it. \n\nFancy Jasper helps those suffering from depression, as it brings hope and light into the wearer’s life.\n\nThe name “jasper” comes from the Greek word for spotted stone. Fancy Jasper is a type of jasper that has unique patterns and colors. It is found in many different locations around the world, including Australia, Brazil, Canada, China, France, Germany, India, Italy, Russia, Spain, Switzerland, and the United States. \n\nImage by Indiamart.com\n\n## Benefits of Fancy Jasper\n\n• Helps go through major life changes with ease\n• Aids in organizing one’s thoughts and ideas\n• Encourages one to follow their dreams\n• Supports during times of stress\n• Promotes feelings of tranquility and peace\n• Soothes the emotions\n• Connects one with the Earth’s energies\n• Assists in problem solving\n• Encourages honesty and fairness\n\n## Fancy Jasper and the chakra connection\n\nFancy Jasper is a stone that is said to be connected to all of the chakras. It is said to be a stone of balance and stability and can help to ground and calm the wearer. While this stone connects to most of the energy points in our body, it connects the most with the root chakra. \n\nThis chakra is located at the base of our spine and is said to be responsible for our sense of safety and security. It is also said to be connected to our survival instincts and our ability to trust our gut instinct.\n\nFancy Jasper is a stone that can help us to feel more connected to the Earth and our bodies. It can help us to feel more grounded and stable, while also providing a sense of calmness and peace. \n\nThis stone can be helpful for those who are feeling scattered or disconnected from their physical body. Fancy Jasper can also be helpful in promoting self-discipline, as well as assisting in decision-making.\n\n## Healing benefits of Fancy Jasper\n\nFancy Jasper is a magical stone and is known as the supreme nurturer. It provides comfort and security, stability and balance, healing and wholeness. Apart from being an emotional and physical healer, it is also known for its metaphysical properties.\n\n## Emotional healing benefits of Fancy Jasper\n\nFancy Jasper is an excellent emotional healer as it helps to soothe and calm emotions. It is a very supportive stone that helps you to feel more stable, balanced and centred. When you go through a tough phase in your life, it often becomes very difficult to think clearly and make rational decisions. \n\nIn such times, Fancy Jasper can be very helpful as it helps to ground you and gives you the strength to face challenges. It also helps to get rid of negative emotions such as anger, fear, anxiety and stress.\n\nThe feeling of fear and guilt are caused due to negative past experiences or traumas. Fancy Jasper can help to release these emotions and also help to heal old wounds. It is a very comforting stone that helps you to feel safe and secure.\n\n## Physical healing benefits of Fancy Jasper\n\nFancy Jasper is known for its physical healing properties. It is said to be helpful in treating disorders of the digestive system and the nervous system. It helps in treating problems related to the eyes, ears, skin and hair. It is also said to be beneficial in boosting the immune system.\n\nFor those who feel tired all the time and suffer from chronic fatigue, Fancy Jasper can be very helpful. It helps to increase energy levels and also provides strength and stamina. It is also said to be helpful in treating sexual problems and impotency.\n\n## Metaphysical properties of Fancy Jasper:\n\nThose who know how magical metaphysical healing properties are will definitely be aware of the Fancy Jasper stone. Fancy Jasper has the ability to connect with all the energy points in the body and cleanse them. It also helps to stabilize the aura and to align the chakras. But most of all, it aligns the root chakra. \n\nThe root chakra is located at the base of the spine and is responsible for our feeling of safety and security. The energy from mother earth enters our body through the root chakra and gives us a sense of grounding. \n\nWhen the root chakra is out of balance, we can feel disconnected from the world around us, anxious and stressed.\n\nFancy Jasper is a very powerful stone when it comes to balancing the root chakra. It helps to ground us and to feel more connected to mother earth. It also provides a sense of stability and security. In addition, Fancy Jasper also has the ability to cleanse and align all the other chakras in the body. \n\n## What are the different ways to use Fancy Jasper?\n\nAs a Meditation stone\n\nFancy Jasper is a stone of Tranquility. It can be used to calm the mind and bring about a sense of inner peace. Using it while meditation is one of the best uses. \n\nWhen you begin the meditation, place the stone in your non-dominant hand and allow it to bring you into a state of relaxation. Bring your focus to the stone once in a while and feel its energy. Using Fancy Jasper while meditation will deepen your connection to the Earth and increase your spiritual awareness.\n\nAs Protection stone\n\nFancy Jasper is also a stone of protection. It can be used to create an energy shield around you that will protect you from negative energies. It is also said to be helpful in warding off evil spirits.\n\nTo use it for protection, carry the stone with you or keep it in your home in a place where you feel it will be most effective.\n\nAs a Fashion accessory\n\nFancy Jasper can also be used as a fashion accessory. It can be made into jewelry or used as decoration on clothing or bags. Using Fancy Jasper as jewelry is a great way to show off your personal style and adds a touch of luxury to your look.\n\nMy personal favorite is the Fancy Jasper bracelet. This bracelet brings a touch of luxury to your look. It can be worn with any outfit and is perfect for any occasion. It remains closest to the body throughout the day, infusing you with Fancy Jasper’s energies.\n\nAs a worry stone\n\nFancy Jasper is also known as a worry stone. It can be used to relieve stress and anxiety. To use it, hold the stone in your hand and rub it with your thumb. Focus on your worries and concerns while you do this. As you rub the stone, feel your worries dissipating.\n\nAs a healing stone\n\nFancy Jasper is also said to be a healing stone. It is said to be helpful in treating a variety of ailments, including stomach problems, skin disorders, and headaches. It is also said to be helpful in promoting restful sleep.\n\nTo use Fancy Jasper for healing, place the stone on the area of the body that needs healing or hold it in your hand while you meditate on the issue.\n\n## Ways to cleanse Fancy Jasper\n\nThere are many ways to cleanse Fancy Jasper. Some of the most popular methods are using running water, using a selenite wand, or using sage smoke.\n\nRunning water\n\nThe best way to cleanse Fancy Jasper is by using running water. Simply hold the stone under running water for a few minutes. You can use any type of water, but many people prefer to use distilled water, holy water, or even ocean water.\n\nSelenite wand\n\nAnother great way to cleanse Fancy Jasper is by using a selenite wand. Simply pass the stone through the selenite wand a few times.\n\nSage smoke\n\nSage smoke is also an excellent way to cleanse Fancy Jasper. Hold the stone over sage smoke for a few minutes. This will help to remove any negative energy from the stone.\n\nMoonlight\n\nMoonlight is also a great way to cleanse Fancy Jasper. This is one of the most gentle ways to cleanse your crystal. Moonlight has feminine energy which will help to cleanse and recharge your Fancy Jasper.\n\nPlace the crystal under full moonlight overnight and remove it the next morning, Your crystal is now ready to be used.\n\n## Best stone combinations to use with Fancy Jasper\n\nFancy Jasper can be combined with a variety of other stones to create beautiful and unique jewelry pieces. Here are some of the best combinations:\n\nFancy Jasper and Blue Topaz\n\nThis combination is said to represent loyalty and friendship. The blue topaz is said to bring calm and serenity, while the Fancy Jasper is said to bring energy and enthusiasm. This makes for a great combination for those who want to feel more balanced and at peace.\n\nFancy Jasper and Citrine\n\nThis combination implies joy and happiness. The citrine is a stone of positivity and optimism, while the Fancy Jasper brings energy and enthusiasm. Both of them together make a great combination for those who want to feel more joyful and positive.\n\nFancy Jasper and Garnet\n\nThese two together represent passion and love. The garnet brings passion and energy, while the Fancy Jasper is said to bring stability and security. This makes for a great combination for those who want to feel more balanced in their relationships.\n\nEnjoyed reading about Fancy Jasper? Here is another healing crystal – Pink Agate which might interest you \n\nFeatured image by Indiamart.com"
  gem.description = "All Jasper crystals are excellent nurturing stones. Fancy Jasper is no different. It is a crystal filled with healing benefits. Fancy Jasper meaning stands for relaxation and contentment, providing comfort and security, strength and healing. Its steady frequency calms the mind and grounds the emotions. It is a wonderful support for those who are prone … Read more"
