otential names, check the availability of domain names and social media handles associated with each option. It’s crucial to have a consistent online presence that matches your store’s name.\n\nAssess for Uniqueness: Research existing sneaker stores and businesses in your area or industry to ensure that your chosen name is distinct and not easily confused with competitors. You want a name that stands out and is memorable.\n\nTest It Out: Share your top name choices with friends, family, or potential cu"
