f roofing companies\n\nThere are different types of roofing companies based on the scope of their services, their specialities, and their target market. Here are some of the most common types of roofing companies:\n\nResidential roofing companies – specialize in roofing services for residential properties.\n\nCommercial roofing companies – specialize in roofing service"
